data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom ranch in the heart of Pulaski, located close to schools and parks. This 3 year young home has lots to offer with the open concept design. The kitchen features SS appliances, center island,  sliding doors that lead to the big backyard, and is open to the living room that offers an updated gas fireplace that is flanked by floating shelves and cabinetry. The spacious primary suite features a walk-in closet and en suite. Head downstairs to the finished lower level with a rec room, a family room with dry bar area, a 4th bedroom and a full bathroom. Plus there is lots of storage too! Garage is finished and heated. This is a great home that is in move in condition. Don't wait to make an appointment to view this one!
